Pathway explored : REACTOME CARBOXYTERMINAL POST TRANSLATIONAL MODIFICATIONS OF TUBULIN

This pathway contain 41 genes.

In these 41 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes in the enrichment.

D4_sCs
6
Tuba1b, Tuba4a, Tubb6 , Tubb4b, Tuba1c, Ttll7
